== Professional influences ==

Chris Hughes learned hypnosis from Gerald F. Kein from the Omni Hypnosis Training Centre<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.omnihypnosis.org|title=OMNIHYPNOSIS – The Home of Modern Hypnosis, Gerald (Jerry) Kein, OMNI training, Hypnotherapy, Hansruedi Wipf|website=www.omnihypnosis.org}}</ref> in Florida. Kein is an American hypnotist and the creator of Ultra-Height Hypnosis.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultraheight.com|title=Products – OMNIHYPNOSIS|website=www.ultraheight.com}}</ref>

